Source:  Autobiography of a Maori
Author:  KOHERE
Vol / Page:  102
Edition:
Quote:  Many a Te Aute boy has been said to have

"gone to the mat," or to have answered

"the call of the wilds," because, after

receiving a college education, he has

gone back to the pa, making little or no

use of his education.
